Repository updates for release
==============================

- Create a jira ticket for tracking
- Triage build for problems
- Change VERSION string to be a *.1-dev developer release
- Update content as needed.
-

repo:ci-management jjb/
-----------------------

- Create a branch or tag repository
- Update .gitreview, set `defaultbranch= <https://gerrit.opencord.org/c/voltha-docs/+/33950/1/.gitreview>`_

repo:voltha-lib-go
------------------

- make sterile distclean
- find . ! -path './vendor/*' -name '*.go' -print0 | xargs -0 gofmt -s -w
- make mod-update
- make lint
- make help
